  "title": "Technical and Construction Supervisor",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate and oversee structural construction activities and technical supervision on-site.</li>\n  <li>Supervise building works to ensure proper execution and progress.</li>\n  <li>Liaise effectively with consultants and subcontractors to resolve issues and maintain workflow.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of work completed on site.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all work meets the required quality standards and conforms to project specifications.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Professional Certificate/Diploma in Civil/ Structural Engineering or equivalent preferable.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
